item.title: 25 Before 25
item.description: New Years Resolutions are no longer the in thing. I recently turned 22 and it feels like my life is whizzing by now. I’ve been thinking about my goals but there are just too many that I have for one year and a couple that will go beyond 2017. So I figured a 25 before 25 would be appropriate. 1. Graduate from university I’ve been in university since I was 17.
